{"type":"text","timestamp":1773483810583,"sessionID":"ses_3142777b4ffe3IuXz7qBZaextx","part":{"id":"prt_cebdf3827001i6LKD8bk5D0OgA","sessionID":"ses_3142777b4ffe3IuXz7qBZaextx","messageID":"msg_cebdf2f82001e0prriS2wylt2M","type":"text","text":"All tasks complete. Here's a summary of what was implemented across all 4 commits:\n\n## Summary of Changes\n\n### 1. Task Browser detail pane (`tui-browser.ts`) — `028d3fc` (pre-existing)\n- Added per-task token usage display showing input/output/cache/reasoning tokens, total tokens, cost, and step count\n- Data loaded from `usage.jsonl` via `loadUsageRecords()` and grouped by `task_id`\n- Added `formatTokenCount()` and `formatCost()` helper functions\n\n### 2. Quest Picker detail pane (`tui-quest-picker.ts`) — `2c49d37`\n- Added `questUsage` and `overallUsage` fields to the `QuestPicker` class\n- Added `reloadUsage()` method that loads records and groups by `quest_id`\n- Added per-quest token usage section in the detail pane (input/output/cache/reasoning/total/cost/steps)\n- Added overall usage totals to the \"All Tasks\" detail view\n- Added `formatTokenCount()` and `formatCost()` helpers\n\n### 3. Usage overlay (`tui-usage-overlay.ts` + `tui-browser.ts`) — `443cfeb`\n- Created new `UsageOverlay` class as a modal overlay (follows `WishlistOverlay` pattern)\n- Shows overall usage summary at top and per-group breakdown in a scrollable list\n- Groups sorted by total tokens descending\n- Tab key cycles grouping between task_id → quest_id → model → provider\n- Escape/U to close\n- Wired U keybind into Task Browser with hint in status bar\n\n### 4. Wave monitor header (`tui.ts`) — `358ee39`\n- Added live aggregate token count and cost to the wave monitor header (from `ProcessMonitor.tokenCollector`)\n- Added per-agent token totals in the agent list rows\n- Uses real-time data from in-memory `TokenCollector` (not disk reads)","time":{"start":1773483810582,"end":1773483810582}}}
